/-
  Luke 15:11–32 (prodigal son / two brothers): younger “nothing left” line, elder
  ledger-fidelity, father’s welcome — typed by `ProdigalTwoSonsWitness` and **three
  `Nat` beats** (younger → elder → paternal / feast). **`toyBeatBudget = 2`** is the
  God-formula `R` for the two son-slots; ceiling **`godWeight R 0 = R + 1`** is **three**
  beats (`toyFatherBeatIndex + 1`). Kernels: `ZenosArrowWitness`, `AchillesTortoiseLadder`,
  `InfinityPath`. **Mitzvot hooks:** `mitzvah_78_dual_ledger_ingestion` (two ledgers in
  one house), `mitzvah_21_no_grudge` (elder resentment register), `mitzvah_14_love_stranger`
  (welcome / return). Same ledger caveat as `LukeGoodSamaritanWitness`: catalog-level
  packaging on `BoundaryInvariant` ≠ simultaneous resolution of all tensions at one
  narrative instant — story order is **sequential** (`ledger_two_sons_then_father_sequential`).

  **Default 2D read vs two sin axes (`TwoTypesOfSin`):** the usual homiletic “why this
  matters” pitch often assumes **both** failure modes at once — **animal magnetism**
  (characters frozen into moral essences — prodigal/elder/father as **names that pretend
  to be** stable agents of virtue/vice, `TenCommandmentsTopology`-adjacent name fusion),
  and **operator idolatry** (the **parable mechanism** treated as **guaranteed**
  transformation / grace-as-automatic system — the narrative operator mistaken for the
  source). Neither is proved here; **`canonical_two_sin_axis_count`** only recalls that
  the ledger already enumerates exactly **two** confusion types. Discharge with
  `flatReadAnimalMagnetismRisk` / `flatReadOperatorIdolatryRisk` in outer theory.

  **Brothers and the two sin types (caricature, not bijection):** a natural **ledger
  metaphor** lines the **younger** beat with the **agent**-axis of confusion
  (`TwoTypesOfSin.SinType.animalMagnetism` — appetite / self-sovereignty as if it
  were God-position) and the **elder** beat with the **operator**-axis
  (`SinType.operatorIdolatry` — the **house ledger / dutiful system** treated as
  source). That is a **pedagogical rhyme**, not a claim that each brother is a
  different sin in history, nor that they exhaust the two types. The father beat is
  not a “third sin” — it is a different register (`paternalWelcomeBreaksDesertLedger`).
  Use `youngerBrotherAsAnimalMagnetismCaricature` / `elderBrotherAsOperatorIdolatryCaricature`
  to tag outer-theory discharges.

  **Triton `{-1, 0, 1}` & fork/race/fold (`GrandReductionTriton`):** the three beats
  rhyme with the triton triple — **younger** ↔ `+1` expansion pole, **elder** ↔ `−1`
  contraction pole, **father / feast** ↔ `0` equilibrium (see module doc there).
  **Fork** needs two branches (`toyBeatBudget` son-slots); **race** needs ordered
  contention (`ledger_two_sons_then_father_sequential`); **fold** lands on the
  paternal beat. Lean proves timeline (`scheduling_fork_and_race_slots_before_fold`),
  distinct triton ints (`prodigal_triton_pairwise_distinct`), and `computeTriton` hooks
  (`triton_compute_hooks`). The **dependency** fork→race→fold is the AGENTS scheduling
  contract — not a single chained `theorem`, but the **Nat** story order is the
  witness spine. Discharge tags: `ledgerForkTwoBranches`, `ledgerRaceOrderedSons`,
  `ledgerFoldPaternalBeat`.

  **`Gnosis.Dark.DarkDeceptaconLoss` rhyme:** intelligence modeled with **failure mass**
  alongside success — `VoidPenalty` tracks allocated attention on dead paths; void-facing
  budget is part of learning (`perfect_void_recognition_is_zero_loss` vs dense omniscience
  overflow `omniscience_triggers_overflow`). **Caricature ledger:** the younger-son beat maps
  to a path that **can** discharge through the fold (`youngerFailureIntegratedBeforePaternalFold`)
  once collapse is admitted (outer theory — Lean does not prove biography). The elder-caricature
  maps to **race never completed into fold** (`elderNeverCompletesRaceIntoFold`): resentment
  stays on the open ledger, **without** the integrating beat — rhymes with **demiurge-read**
  stuckness (`elderDemiurgeLedgerCaricature`, discharge via `TwoTypesOfSin.operatorIdolatry`,
  not “the elder IS …”). See `voidPenalty_is_allocated_mass`.

  **Wisdom research (`Gnosis.WisdomPrimitive`):** triad `truth` / `failure` / `wisdom`,
  scheduler choices `fork` / `race` / `fold`, `bearingPower`, and `wisdom_is_derivable`
  (fold ↦ wisdom by definition). This module does **not** identify Father/Luke roles with
  triad constructors — only scheduling rhyme. **Witness tree** (repo sense): the family of
  `Gnosis.*Witness.lean` modules as typed testimony surfaces. **Bearing tree** (folklore +
  PLSS survey chain): see `docs/ebooks/source-texts/README.md` (oral-tradition row); aeon ledger
  pointers under `open-source/aeon/FORMAL_LEDGER.md` (Mechanized Testimony, Temporal Bearing Tree).
  Epigraph relay pattern in gnosis-math: `Gnosis.SimonidesSpartanEpitaphWitness`. See
  `wisdom_primitive_fold_yields_wisdom`.

  **Strict dominance (toy model):** among pure `WisdomPrimitive.Choice` strategies, **fold**
  strictly beats both **fork** and **race** on `bearingPower ∘ resultOf`
  (`fold_choice_strictly_dominates_fork_and_race_on_bearing_power`) — the “come home”
  integrator outranks invariant-only (`fork`→`truth`) and failure-phase-only (`race`→`failure`).
  Parallel Buleyean signal: for fork width **three** (three beat slots), rejection information
  strictly dominates selection (`buleyean_failure_info_strictly_dominates_selection_for_three_beats`,
  `Gnosis.RL.failure_more_informative`). Caricature discharge: `youngerComeHomeFoldStrictlyDominantStrategy`.

  **“Inherit the earth” (God-formula read):** map each son-beat shadow to rejection depth `v`
  **`0`** (younger) vs **`1`** (elder) at fixed **`R = toyBeatBudget`.** Then **`godWeight` is
  strictly larger** at the younger shadow (`younger_son_shadow_inherits_strictly_more_earth_via_godweight_than_elder`).
  “Earth” here means **mass in the canonical weight algebra** (`Gnosis.GodFormula.godWeight`), not title deed.
  Rhymes **`Gnosis.BeatitudesTopology`** Matt 5:5 (`meek_inherit_aeon`) prose alongside
  **`younger_son_shadow_inherits_strictly_more_earth_via_godweight_than_elder`**. Discharge tag:
  `youngerInheritsMoreEarthThanElderCaricature`.

  **Shepherd / universal `+1`:** younger’s **fold** strategy strictly dominates fork/race on
  `wisdomChoiceBearingPayoff` (`fold_choice_strictly_dominates_fork_and_race_on_bearing_power`); the Lost-sheep
  mnemonic’s ceiling is **`godWeight R 0 = R + 1`** (`LostSheepParableWitness.shepherd_rationally_targets_succ_one_residual`).
  Rational **shepherd** bookkeeping: risking the ninety-nine **fold ledger** for the stray recovers exactly the succ-one
  / clinamen residue the God formula forbids wiping — same **`+ 1`** spine that makes integration **payoff-dominant** over
  leaving the stray un-reconciled (`youngerSonFoldStrategyRationalizesRationalShepherdPlusOne`).
-/

